#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bohr Orbitals"
msgstr "Aatomimudel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Atom Model</guilabel> page displays the atomic shells. Every "
"orbit stands for a atomic shell and every yellow circle represents an "
"electron."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Aatomimudel</guilabel> näeb aatomi ehitust. Iga orbiit "
"tähistab orbitaali ja iga kollane ringike elektroni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Isotopes"
msgstr "Isotoobid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Isotopes</guilabel> page presents information about the "
"isotopes of an element."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Isotoobid</guilabel> näeb teavet elemendi isotoopide kohta."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mass"
msgstr "Mass"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "The mass of this isotope."
msgstr "Isotoobi mass."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Neutrons"
msgstr "Neutronid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of neutrons this isotope has."
msgstr "Isotoobi neutronite arv."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Percentage"
msgstr "Protsent"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The percentage of atoms occurring that are of this isotope type. Also called "
"abundance."
msgstr "Antud tüüpi isotoobi aatomite esinemissagedus."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Half-life period"
msgstr "Poolestumisaeg"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only unstable isotopes have a half-life period. It is defined as the time in "
"which half the isotopes decay."
msgstr ""
"Poolestumisaeg on omane ainult ebastabiilsetele isotoopidele ja see tähendab "
"aega, mille jooksul pooled isotoobid lagunevad."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Energy and Mode of Decay"
msgstr "Lagunemise tüüp ja energia"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some isotopes are known to emit particle radiation under the process of "
"radioactive decay. Each decay transformation has a typical energy release, "
"which is listed along with the mode of decay."
msgstr ""
"Mõned isotoobid emiteerivad radioaktiivse lagunemise käigus osakesi. Igal "
"lagunemisel vabaneb teatud kogus energiat, mis ongi siin kirjas koos "
"lagunemise tüübiga."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spin and Parity"
msgstr "Spinn ja paarsus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "The spin of the nucleus and its parity."
msgstr "Tuuma spinn ja paarsus."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Magnetic Moment"
msgstr "Magnetmoment"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The magnetic dipole moment of the nucleus. Measured in units of the nuclear "
"magneton."
msgstr "Tuuma magnetmoment."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Muu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Miscellaneous</guilabel> page tells you other information "
"about the current element, including when it was discovered and the origin "
"of the name."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Muu</guilabel> leiab veel mitmesugust teavet elemendi "
"kohta, sealhulgas seda, millal see avastati ja mille järgi on see nime "
"saanud."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spectrum"
msgstr "Spekter"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Spectrum</guilabel> page shows you elements spectrum. You can "
"choose the range of the wavelengths, units and type of the spectrum. The "
"intensity table can be seen at the right bottom part of the page."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Spekter</guilabel> näeb elemendi spektrit. Seal saab "
"valida lainepikkuste vahemiku, ühikud ja spektri tüübi. Intensiivsustabelit "
"näeb kaardil all paremal."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extra Information"
msgstr "Lisateave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Extra information</guilabel> page gives you the links to "
#| "the element pages on Wikipedia, <ulink url=\"http://education.jlab.org/"
#| "\">Jefferson Lab</ulink>, and <ulink url=\"http://www.webelements.com/"
#| "\">WebElements</ulink>."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Extra information</guilabel> page gives you the links to the "
"element pages on Wikipedia, <ulink url=\"https://education.jlab.org/"
"\">Jefferson Lab</ulink>, and <ulink url=\"https://www.webelements.com/"
"\">WebElements</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Lisateave</guilabel> on ära toodud lingid elemendi "
"leheküljele Wikipedias, <ulink url=\"http://education.jlab.org/\">Jefferson "
"Labis</ulink> ja <ulink url=\"http://www.webelements.com/\">WebElementsis</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:323 index.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tables"
msgstr "Tabelid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The periodic table can be presented in various ways. You can switch the "
"table view from <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu or toolbar drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Perioodilisustabelit saab kuvada mitmel moel. Tabeli vaadet saab muuta kas "
"menüüst <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> või tööriistariba rippmenüüst."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The following options in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Tables</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu can be used to change "
#| "the table shown:"
msgid ""
"The following options in the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Tables</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu can be used to change the "
"table shown:"
msgstr ""
"Näidatava tabeli muutmiseks saab kasutada menüüs <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> "
"<guimenu>Tabelid</guimenu> järgmisi võimalusi:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:330
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
