"<guilabel>Statistika</guilabel> paneel näitab molekuli nime (kui see on "
"olemas), valemit ja massi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Display</guilabel> tab can be used to view a loaded molecule. "
"By pressing the mouse pointer in the view, you can change the view point. "
"Use &LMB; to rotate molecule, &RMB; to move it, and &MMB; to zoom."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Kuvamine</guilabel> saab nöha laaditud molekuli. &HVNga; "
"saab molekuli pöörata, &HPNga; liigutada ja &HKNga; suurendada või vähendada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Edit</guilabel> tab allows you to edit the molecule. You can "
"add elements by choosing them in the <guilabel>Element</guilabel> drop-down "
"list then clicking with the &LMB; on the view panel on the right."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Muutmine</guilabel> on võimalik muuta molekuli. Soovi "
"korral saab lisada elemente, valides need rippmenüüst <guilabel>Element</"
"guilabel> ja klõpsates &HVNga; vaatepaneelil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Measure</guilabel> tab can be used to measure distances and "
"angles in the molecule. To make the measurement use the instructions shown "
"on the tab."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Mõõtmine</guilabel> saab mõõta molekuli vahemaid ja nurki. "
"Mõõtmiseks kasuta kaardil näidatavaid juhiseid."

