#, no-c-format
msgid "Theoretical Equations"
msgstr "Teoreetilised võrrandid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can fill the table with the equations you have previously obtained "
"for the chemical equilibrium."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab täita tabeli võrranditega, mille oled varem keemilise tasakaalu "
"kohta hankinud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, if you have this reaction <emphasis>A + B -> C + D</emphasis> "
"then you will have the equation <emphasis>K=(C*D)/(A*B)</emphasis> so you "
"must write <userinput>K</userinput> in the <guilabel>Parameter</guilabel> "
"column and <userinput>(C*D)/(A*B)</userinput> in the <guilabel>Value</"
"guilabel> column. If you want to assign a known value to a parameter you can "
"simply write the numeric value in the <guilabel>Value</guilabel> field."
msgstr ""
"Kui sul on näiteks tegemist reaktsiooniga <emphasis>A + B -> C + D</"
"emphasis>, siis on võrrand <emphasis>K=(C*D)/(A*B)</emphasis>, nii et tuleb "
"kirjutada <userinput>K</userinput> veergu <guilabel>Parameeter</guilabel> ja "
"<userinput>(C*D)/(A*B)</userinput> veergu <guilabel>Väärtus</guilabel>. Kui "
"soovid omistada parameetrile teadaoleva väärtuse, võid ka lihtsalt kirjutada "
"arvväärtuse veergu <guilabel>Väärtus</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid "For example, you can use the system"
msgstr "Näiteks võib kasutada süsteemi"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "A=(C*D)/(B*K)"
msgstr "A=(C*D)/(B*K)"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid "K=10^-3"
msgstr "K=10^-3"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "C=OH"
msgstr "C=OH"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid "OH=(10^-14)/H"
msgstr "OH=(10^-14)/H"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid "H=10^-4"
msgstr "H=10^-4"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid "B=6*(10^-2)"
msgstr "B=6*(10^-2)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:707
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Then you have to write <userinput>D</userinput> as <guilabel>X axis</"
